# Dashboard product analytics (PostHog) for the React SPA. Copy to .env.local
# and fill in to enable; leave unset to disable (the dashboard runs unchanged).
#
# VITE_ vars are inlined into the SPA bundle at BUILD time, so they must be
# present on the machine that runs `npm run build` / `npm run deploy` — they
# are not `wrangler secret`s. The key is a public, write-only PostHog project
# API key (phc_...); the Worker uses the same value via POSTHOG_KEY.
VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=
VITE_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com
